This will be my notes to manage my scala code.
1) Create directory first
2) Create a project 
	sbt new scala/hello-world.g8 #Creates a simple project
	name the application
3) Run the code by:
	a) Enter the project dir example "hello-world"
	b) Enter "sbt" to run sbt
4) Modify the code by:
	a) Enter the dir src/main/scala/Main.scala
	b) Edit with notepad/nano
	c) Do step 3

